<b>IBM research and development activities in <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../173/9282173.xml">
Israel</link></country>
</b> include the following labs. 
</p>
<sec>
<st>
 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/research.html">
<b>Haifa Research Lab</b></weblink> </st>
<p>

<b>HRL</b> handles projects in the spheres of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../494/19541494.xml">
cloud computing</link><weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/nov2007/tc20071116_379585.htm">
http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/nov2007/tc20071116_379585.htm</weblink> <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www-03.ibm.com/press/us/en/pressrelease/23448.wss">
http://www-03.ibm.com/press/us/en/pressrelease/23448.wss</weblink>,<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../925/261925.xml">
healthcare</link>, and life sciences, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../989/665989.xml">
verification technologies</link> <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/svt/index.html">
http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/svt/index.html</weblink> <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/vst/index.html">
http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/vst/index.html</weblink>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../420/20420.xml">
multimedia</link>, active management <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/services/stes.html">
http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/services/stes.html</weblink>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../271/15271.xml">
information retrieval</link> <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/imt/ir.html">
http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/imt/ir.html</weblink>, programming environments <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.ibm.com/dept/services/index.html">
http://www.haifa.ibm.com/dept/services/index.html</weblink>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../691/1155691.xml">
business transformation</link>, and optimization technologies <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/services/abo.html">
http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/dept/services/abo.html</weblink>. HRL is the biggest <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../666/551666.xml">
IBM research center</link> outside the US.</p>

</sec>
<sec>
<st>
 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/info/20080416_stg.shtml">
<b>Systems and Technology Group Lab</b></weblink> </st>
<p>

<b>STG</b> incorporates the former <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.il.ibm.com/development.html">
Haifa Development Lab</weblink>. STG provides design services for <arrangement wordnetid="107938773" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<array wordnetid="107939382" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../845/147845.xml">
ASIC</link></array>
</group>
</arrangement>
 logic design, full custom digital and analog <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../344/2848344.xml">
circuit design</link>, array design, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../586/13475586.xml">
physical design</link>, design verification services, chip design and verification, new IP, advanced architecture, synthesis, and lab testing. The lab also develops functions for IBM storage controllers, including an entire set of replication functions for storage systems <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.haifa.ibm.com/development/storage.shtml">
http://www.haifa.ibm.com/development/storage.shtml</weblink> for flash copy, concurrent copy, extended remote copy, peer-to-peer remote copy, and storage management.</p>

